n
2^{n-1}-{1 \over 2} {\left( n \atop {n/2}\right)}
(a+b)^n=\sum_{k=0}^n  {\left( n \atop {k}\right)} a^k b^{n-k}
a=b=1
2^n=\sum_{k=0}^n  {\left( n \atop {k}\right)}
  {\left( n \atop {k}\right)}={\left( n \atop {n-k}\right)}
2^{n-1}
{1 \over 2}\left[\sum_{k=0}^n  {\left( n \atop {k}\right)} -{\left( n \atop {n/2}\right)}\right]= 2^{n-1}-{1 \over 2} {\left( n \atop {n/2}\right)} 
